    {
      "section_id": "para_54",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "An  Act  to  provide  for  the  re-computation  of  pensions,  gratuities \nand other benefits for officers in the public service, who are subject \nto  the  salaries  and  terms  and  conditions  of  service  based  on  the \nrecommendations  by  the  Suffian  and  Aziz  Royal  Commissions, \nand  their  dependants.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_55",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "[1  August  1968]",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_56",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "BE   IT   ENACTED   by   the   Seri   Paduka   Baginda   Yang   di- \nPertuan  Agong  with  the  advice  and  consent  of  the  Dewan \nNegara  and  Dewan  Rakyat  in  Parliament  assembled,  and  by  the \nauthority of  the  same,  as  follows:",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
