      "heading": "1.  This  Act  may  be  cited  as  the  Pensions  Re-computation  Act \n1980  and  shall  be  deemed  to  have  come  into  force  on  1  August \n1968.",
      "content": "1.  This  Act  may  be  cited  as  the  Pensions  Re-computation  Act \n1980  and  shall  be  deemed  to  have  come  into  force  on  1  August \n1968.",
